name: humble-chasing-goose
description: Add documentation comments to types.rs and events.rs

members.name: docs-types
members.prompt:
Add a module-level doc comment to src/types.rs:

1. Read src/types.rs to understand its contents
2. Add a brief `//!` doc comment (2-3 lines max) at the top describing that this module contains PRD, Story, DroneStatus and other shared types for Hive
3. Run `cargo build` to verify it compiles
4. Run `cargo clippy` to verify linting passes

When done, notify the team-lead that the task is complete.

members.name: docs-events
members.prompt:
Add a module-level doc comment to src/events.rs:

1. Read src/events.rs to understand its contents
2. Add a brief `//!` doc comment (2-3 lines max) at the top describing that this module handles HiveEvent and EventReader for TUI monitoring
3. Run `cargo build` to verify it compiles
4. Run `cargo clippy` to verify linting passes

When done, notify the team-lead that the task is complete.
